8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode Three=

11
00:00:45,119 --> 00:00:45,920
Stop!

12
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:17,200
(Two of my sons are fighting for her.)

13
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,560
(That's rather interesting.)

14
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,719
Pass down my decree.

15
00:01:21,159 --> 00:01:23,879
Confer Mei Lin of Xichu
as Princess Anhe.

16
00:01:24,159 --> 00:01:26,280
All Xichu slaves are to be pardoned

17
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,799
to display our grace.

18
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:30,200
- Thank you, Your Majesty!
- Thank you, Your Majesty!

19
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:31,599
Your Majesty

20
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:34,079
she's a surrendered slave of Xichu.

21
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,200
Her identity is unclear.

22
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,200
What if she's an assassin sent here?

23
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:37,879
Wouldn't that be...?

24
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:38,799
Father, please

25
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,799
allow me to investigate

26
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,319
her identity and find out the truth.

27
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:44,680
Fine.

28
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,640
Let Mei Lin remain
in the palace for now.

29
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:49,319
Pei Du, you'll investigate her.

30
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,640
If her identity is confirmed

31
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:51,760
proceed with the conferment.

32
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:54,920
Thank you, Your Majesty.

33
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,280
You're dismissed.

34
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,479
(Princess Mei Lin of Xichu,)

35
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:17,360
(time to learn court etiquette.)

36
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,199
My lady

37
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:28,960
I was sent here to teach you
the proper decorum.

38
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,759
A baseborn slave from Xichu indeed.

39
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,960
Such a bad learner.

40
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:50,960
What are you up to?

41
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,319
If you dare provoke me again

42
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:53,120
I'll kill you.

43
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,919
You wouldn't dare!

44
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,000
Then try me.

45
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,000
M-My lady

46
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:01,840
I... I'm sorry.

47
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,280
I'll never do it again.

48
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,639
Please let me go, my lady.

49
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:10,159
Tell me everything about Consort Chu.

50
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:12,199
Every detail and preference as hers.

51
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:14,240
If you miss even one thing,
I will kill you.

52
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:17,120
No, don't!
I will tell you everything I know!

53
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,319
Someone.

54
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:23,840
Bind my hair.

55
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,199
Jinghe.

56
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:04,520
Your Highness,
you made me play the princess.

57
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,960
Did I pass this test?

58
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:13,759
Your face? Maybe. Your behavior? No.

59
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:19,399
So you admit my appearance is good?

60
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:24,800
Good or bad, let's see if you can use it

61
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:27,160
to capture Prince Xuanlie's heart.

62
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,879
Princess Mei Lin.

63
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,240
Your Highness.

64
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,319
Don't be afraid.

65
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,120
I came specially to see you.

66
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:46,759
You look alike.

67
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,839
You really do.

68
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,560
(Even this fragrance...
It is the same of hers.)

69
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:56,839
(Cedar fragrance.)

70
00:04:57,519 --> 00:04:59,639
(Why does Prince Xuanlie
wear that scent?)

71
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:02,680
(Could he be the head
of the Shadow Bureau?)

72
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:05,160
May I ask, Your Highness

73
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,319
who is she?

74
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:09,560
An old friend.

75
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,879
If you're curious who she was

76
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:14,000
I'll tell you all about her.

77
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:22,240
Don't disappoint me, little blade.

78
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:27,560
What do you think of these paintings?

79
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:31,839
Masterful technique.

80
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:35,360
But why are there no facial features?

81
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:37,720
Because her beauty

82
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:40,639
cannot be captured by mortal brushwork.

83
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,160
To be honest

84
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:45,800
you resemble my old friend perfectly.

85
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:48,040
ah?

86
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,439
I asked you here today

87
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:51,519
because I have a request to make.

88
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,040
If you need anything

89
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,560
how could I refuse?

90
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:58,480
Come.

91
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,600
Please, sit.

92
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,399
(She's been gone for years.)

93
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:05,639
(Though I still remember her face well,)

94
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,759
(I've never dared to paint her.)

95
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,439
(Today, with your help,)

96
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:12,720
(I will grind the ink and paint)

97
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:15,519
(and finally complete these portraits
in this room.)

98
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,399
Yiyi

99
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:24,480
you've come back.

100
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,759
(It's too good a chance to miss.)

101
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,480
Such deep feelings, Your Highness.

102
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,279
If the woman in the painting knew

103
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,600
she would surely be moved.

104
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:41,959
But...

105
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,600
she's gone now.

106
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,199
Your Highness

107
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:54,000
why not cherish the one before you?

108
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,800
You're quite bold.

109
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:04,160
Only because you allowed me to be.

110
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:44,240
Your Highness, you summoned me so late.

111
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,879
Surely it's not just to watch you
polish your sword.

112
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:49,560
You reek of

113
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:53,560
a scent that disgusts me.

114
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:57,079
Weren't you the one who sent me

115
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:58,879
to spy for you by Prince Xuanlie's side?

116
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,360
Get down here.

117
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:31,060
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

